      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "NOTE: [REDACTED] is not identifiable in Bufiles. Joseph F. Perry of",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Grand Blanc, Michigan, was contacted by Bureau Agents from our",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Detroit Office at his request in March, 1960, regarding photographs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "he had taken of what he believed to be unidentified flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "These photographs were turned over to the Office of Special Investi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "gations of the United States Air Force by our Detroit Office. Perry",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "reported to the local paper that the FBI was conducting an investiga-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
