      "text": "tion and it was necessary for this Bureau to straighten the record",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "with that newspaper. Perry was advised that we had furnished his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
